    "<div style='background:#4a4a4a;color:white;padding:40px;text-align:center;border-radius:10px;'>\n",
    "  <h1 style='color:white;font-weight:bold;margin:0;'>Traffic Sign Recognition</h1>\n",
    "  <h2 style='color:white;margin-top:8px;'>A Deep Learning Approach via GTSRB Dataset</h2>\n",
    "  <hr style='border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);margin:16px 0;'>\n",
    "  <h3 style='color:white;font-weight:bold;margin:0;'>Abdulrahman Ageeli &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Ali Alqarni</h3>\n",
    "  <h4 style='color:white;margin:5px 0 0 0;'>Deep Learning Course &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Supervised by Dr. Majdi Khalid</h4>\n",
    "</div>"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "<div style='background:#4a4a4a;color:white;padding:14px 22px;border-radius:6px;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;'>\n",
    "1 &middot; Introduction & Dataset Structural Analysis\n",
    "</div>\n",
    "\n",
    "<div style='padding:16px 6px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:#000;font-weight:bold;'>\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Dataset Profile:** German Traffic Sign Recognition Benchmark (GTSRB) consisting of 43 distinct classes.\n",
    "- **Real-World Challenges:** Images feature extreme variations in illumination, motion blur, physical occlusions, and scale resolutions.\n",
    "- **The Class Imbalance Problem:** Some classes contain >2000 samples while others have <200 samples. <br>\n",
    "  <span style='color:#b8860b;'>&rarr; Anticipated Faculty Question: How did you prevent the model from biasing towards majority classes?</span><br>\n",
    "  - *Our Defense Strategy:* Handled via **Stratified Dataset Splitting** (maintaining distribution ratios) and applying **Class-Weighted Cross Entropy Loss** to heavily penalize minority class misclassifications.\n",
    "\n",
    "</div>\n",
    "\n",
    "<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top:10px; font-weight:bold; color:#000;'>\n",
    "  <tr style='background:#f2f2f2; border-bottom:2px solid #ccc;'>\n",
    "    <th style='padding:10px; text-align:left;'>Data Subset Partition</th>\n",
    "    <th style='padding:10px; text-align:left;'>Total Samples</th>\n",
    "    <th style='padding:10px; text-align:left;'>Rigorous Engineering Purpose</th>\n",
    "  </tr>\n",
    "  <tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>Train Set</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>31,367</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>Backpropagation and active gradient weight updates.</td>\n",
    "  </tr>\n",
    "  <tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>Validation Set</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>7,842</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>Hyperparameter optimization and Early Stopping enforcement.</td>\n",
    "  </tr>\n",
    "  <tr style='border-bottom:2px solid #ccc;'>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>Test Set</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>12,630</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>Final completely unbiased generalization performance check.</td>\n",
    "  </tr>\n",
    "</table>"
   ]
  },
