    "<div style='background:#4a4a4a;color:white;padding:14px 22px;border-radius:6px;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;'>\n",
    "4 &middot; Model 2: Deep Transfer Learning via ResNet-50\n",
    "</div>\n",
    "\n",
    "<div style='padding:16px 6px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:#000;font-weight:bold;'>\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Strategy:** Implemented Transfer Learning utilizing a heavy ResNet-50 backbone pre-trained on the comprehensive ImageNet corpus (1.28 Million natural images).\n",
    "- **Training Paradigm:** Fixed feature extraction. The entire deep convolutional backbone was completely frozen, while optimization focused exclusively on a newly appended Fully Connected classification head.\n",
    "- **Duration Parameters:** Trained across a brief baseline run of 15 epochs utilizing the exact same optimization hyperparameter metrics for structural parity.\n",
    "\n",
    "</div>"
   ]
