    "<div style='margin-top:15px; padding:14px; background:#eef7f2; border-left:5px solid #27ae60; border-radius:4px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#000; font-weight:bold;'>\n",
    "  <span style='color:#27ae60; font-size:16px;'>&#128161; Critical Analysis - Core Engineering Insight:</span><br>\n",
    "  - **ResNet-50** successfully surpassed the human benchmark (+0.36%) because general visual features (edges, textures, shapes) transfer smoothly across visual domains. Knowledge from 1.28M natural image records directly translates into reading traffic signs.<br>\n",
    "  - **Custom CNN** reached remarkable operational efficiency, pulling within 1.04% of human accuracy while utilizing less than **2%** of ResNet's overall parameter weight. This makes it an ideal architecture for resource-constrained hardware deployments.\n",
